# UdpServer, MIT (c) 2019-2021 miktim@mail.ru
  UDP broadcast/unicast/multicast sender/receiver
  
  Overview:
    Constructors:
      UdpServer(int port, UdpServer.Handler handler) throws IOException; // broadcast
      UdpServer(int port, InetAddress inetAddress, UdpServer.Handler handler) throws IOException;
    
    UdpServer.Handler:
      void onUdpPacket(UdpServer server, DatagramPacket packet);
      void onUdpError(UdpServer server, Exception e);
    
    Methods:
      void start(); // start listening
      void close();
      void send(byte[] packet) throws IOException;
      boolean isListening(); 
      boolean isMulticast();
      DatagramSocket getDatagramSocket();

